CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

September 30, 2009

[Cite as 09/30/2009 Case Announcements, 2009-Ohio-5031.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2009-1288. [State ex rel.] Looper v. Ohio State Univ.

In Mandamus. On relator’s complaint in mandamus and motion for contempt and respondent’s answer. On S.Ct.Prac.R. X(5) determination, cause dismissed. Motion for contempt denied as moot.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
